{"tid":1891390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟最近由An機轉左去Iphone","createTime":"2020-02-21T20:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T02:31:22.000Z","uid":326586,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"43b666dfcfc82955c047a3429485dc1e2c96e686","tid":1891390,"uid":326586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:04:52.000Z","msg":"咁夜麻麻無聊咪張部舊機啲張BackUp順手刪緊啲相，留番做BackUp機。<br />\n<br />\n人就係一樣好得意既生物﹐每當你以為件事/個人已經好徹底咁忘記咗 ﹐但當張相突然之間俾我執相見番以前﹐回憶就好似啲大動脈俾人切斷一樣﹐不停咁Bla Bla聲喺個腦飛出嚟。 <br />\n<br />\n但我回想番起你最後一兩次見我嘅眼神﹐果時我就應該要知道個關係已經唔同咗﹐只不過係當時自己呃自己啫。<br />\n<br />\n一晚睇番曬呢六年嘅相先發現，所有嘢好琴日先發生完。<br />\n<br />\n不論友情，親情，愛情，都會因為一兩件事，甚至一兩句說話就會失去咗。<br />\n<br />\n今晚睇嚟都喺一個失眠夜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">善用不推文回覆，靜靜地放負好喇</span>"},{"pid":"7a5e460f6e0ef209dd271045ac67cc354f93027e","tid":1891390,"uid":296041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:10:10.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"93a496188cd57dc9f18812290390d9a2aabd95fa","tid":1891390,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:11:36.000Z","msg":"An機用到6年？"},{"pid":"c056193908349978307dd1f73281dbd39bfa1fc0","tid":1891390,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a496188cd57dc9f18812290390d9a2aabd95fa","tid":1891390,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:11:36.000Z","msg":"An機用到6年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbdf70282d5921671369cf50b6cc8a68108c7ec","tid":1891390,"uid":326586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a496188cd57dc9f18812290390d9a2aabd95fa","tid":1891390,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:11:36.000Z","msg":"An機用到6年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該喺話用咗咁多年An機，第一次整理啲相"},{"pid":"1c586af007134aeab58c6c841656b27e5623d9fa","tid":1891390,"uid":62648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T21:47:45.000Z","msg":"恭喜加入iphone<br />\n用完iphone返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"0bb7301c11afb2f80376f96f955ea366f5592769","tid":1891390,"uid":11091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"大家既重點都係focus左係部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打我都試過，初初用第一部智能電話都係android，三年前換左iphone，過陣都有睇番曬d相，好多感受會番曬黎，感嘆原來經歷左咁多野，原來咁多朋友已經冇再見面，但慶幸身邊果位仲係身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n信我，下次睇又會唔同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2042214a6dfaa1c42e4d0c7ebe7de77be8deaa","tid":1891390,"uid":336046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T01:28:35.000Z","msg":"所以我一不影相，二不執相<br />\n<br />\n不過我用唔慣iOS 會轉返Android"},{"pid":"5dd473e21771229311e70fe69bf5ddd414d06090","tid":1891390,"uid":321305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93a496188cd57dc9f18812290390d9a2aabd95fa","tid":1891390,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:11:36.000Z","msg":"An機用到6年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T01:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我之前用咗7年"},{"pid":"fef2fc140c0412b418d73d2141c0ce748c1da601","tid":1891390,"uid":309331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"同一個故事 咁就過咗幾年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}